ed shape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon/polygons":{"title":"polygons","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of polygons forming the multipolygon."}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/polygons","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"polygons"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/polygons"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolygon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}],"title":"MLNMultiPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","role":"symbol"}}}